This is *very* fresh code that is still in development.

It's new, please don't judge me on this code just now (although it's not too
bad). You'd be better off looking at something more complete, like:

http://github.com/Spakman/jobby/blob/master/lib/server.rb


BBC radio on demand
===

This library is a small set of classes to make accessing and traversing the BBC
radio on demand (iPlayer for radio, basically) XML feeds. The feeds cover
around seven days of scheduling and are updated every three or so hours (I
think).
